            <scopecontent id="aspace_08d01b183d2cc3856e8a1058dc172879">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Correspondence, subject files, administrative files, financial papers, and films pertaining to Howard Sayre Weaver. The papers appear to have been generated during his tenure as Dean of the School of Art and Architecture, and include materials from the Yale-New Haven Educational Corporation, the Hills Art Co-op, and the New Haven Foundation. The collection has not been fully processed.</p>
